OL,3,CStarmer pledges cost-of-living support
OL,4,Cfor households hit by energy price
OL,5,Cspike
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer will pledge to help
OL,8,Fhouseholds with the cost of living
OL,9,Famid the energy price spike caused by
OL,10,Fthe war in the Middle East.
OL,12,FThe prime minister will on Monday say
OL,13,Fhelping households with living costs
OL,14,Fis "my first priority" as he announces
OL,15,Fa subsidy for people who use heating
OL,16,Foil to heat their homes after war-
OL,17,Fdriven price spikes.
OL,26,@vD@DOUvD@VO]
