OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773709368
OL,3,CStarmer pledges cost-of-living support
OL,4,Cfor households hit by energy price
OL,5,Cspike
OL,7,FStarmer's heating oil announcement on
OL,8,FMonday comes after Chancellor Rachel
OL,9,FReeves said Treasury officials have
OL,10,F"found the money" to help the 1.5
OL,11,Fmillion households relying on the fuel.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
