FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773709368
OL,3,CStarmer pledges cost-of-living support
OL,4,Cfor households hit by energy price
OL,5,Cspike
OL,7,FHeating oil is not protected by the
OL,8,Fenergy price cap, and its price per
OL,9,Flitre has doubled due to disruption to
OL,10,Foil supplies from the Middle East
OL,11,Fsince the US-Israeli war with Iran
OL,12,Fbegan.
OL,14,FInside Downing Street, Starmer will
OL,15,Fsay: "It's moments like this that tell
OL,16,Fyou what a government is about.
OL,18,F"My answer is clear. Whatever
OL,19,Fchallenges lie ahead, this government
OL,20,Fwill always support working people.
OL,26,@wD@FOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
