PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773709368
OL,3,CStarmer pledges cost-of-living support
OL,4,Cfor households hit by energy price
OL,5,Cspike
OL,7,F"That is my first instinct ` my first
OL,8,Fpriority ` to help you with the cost
OL,9,Fof living through this crisis."
OL,11,FThe prime minister will also raise
OL,12,Fconcerns over claims some heating-oil
OL,13,Fsuppliers cancelled orders before
OL,14,Fsharply increasing prices.
OL,16,FLast week, Ms Reeves and Energy
OL,17,FSecretary Ed Miliband met oil firm
OL,18,Fbosses and forecourt operators to warn
OL,19,Fthem against profiteering.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@_O]
