PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773709368
OL,3,CStarmer pledges cost-of-living support
OL,4,Cfor households hit by energy price
OL,5,Cspike
OL,7,FIn his press conference, Starmer will
OL,8,Fsay: "I will not tolerate companies
OL,9,Ftrying to exploit this crisis to make
OL,10,Fmoney from working people... if the
OL,11,Fcompanies have broken the law, there
OL,12,Fwill be legal action."
OL,14,FDe-escalation of the war is the
OL,15,Fquickest way to reduce cost-of-living
OL,16,Fpressures for the British public, the
OL,17,Fprime minister will insist.
OL,26,@pD@FOUtD@VO]
