OL,3,CStarmer pledges cost-of-living support
OL,4,Cfor households hit by energy price
OL,5,Cspike
OL,7,FElsewhere, Foreign Secretary Yvette
OL,8,FCooper has mobilised more than #5
OL,9,Fmillion in aid for humanitarian
OL,10,Forganisations in Lebanon amid fighting
OL,11,Fbetween Israel and the militant group
OL,12,FHezbollah.
OL,14,FShe said she was "gravely concerned
OL,15,Fabout the developing conflict in
OL,16,FLebanon and the scale of the
OL,17,Fhumanitarian impact".
